Documentation of FSS-V1

This is a construction of the FSS (Filter-Stack Spectrometer) project.
Specifically, FSS-V1 is dedicated to Box FSS-A experiments,
but specifics of FSS-B are also listed

The Filter Stacks: 
=== #1. Box FSS-A
    Structure:
        Substructure:   |           |           |
                        |           |           |
                        |           |           |
                        |           |           |
                plastic layer    metal plate    plastic det.
        Component: 19 substructures
    Metal 1~3: Aluminium(Al)    500, 500, 1500 um
    Metal 4~9: Copper(Cu)       500, 500, 1000, 1000, 1500, 2000 um
    Metal 10~11: Tin(Sn)        850, 850 um
    Metal 12~19: Lead(Pb)       1000, 1000, 1000, 1000, 1000, 1000, 3000, 3000 um

=== #2. Box FSS-B
    Structure:
        Substructure:   |           |           |
                        |           |           |
                        |           |           |
                        |           |           |
                plastic layer    metal plate    plastic det.
        Component: 19 substructures
    Metal 1~3: Aluminium(Al)    500, 500, 1500 um
    Metal 4~9: Copper(Cu)       500, 1000, 1000, 1000, 1500, 2000 um
    Metal 10~11: Tin(Sn)        850, 850 um
    Metal 12~19: Lead(Pb)       1000, 1000, 1000, 1000, 1000, 1000, 3000, 3000 um

Plastic Material: Polystyrene ()

World Material: Air (1 m * 1 m * 1 m, Box)


