=== VERY USEFUL Commands for Visualization ===

Expanse SDSC does NOT have visualization UIs, which may be fixed using the following commands
in your local computer. You will need to download freeWRL and apply vrml.mac in your main source file.

1. download the visulization to local computer

scp <YOUR_ID>@login.expanse.sdsc.edu:/home/<YOUR_ID>/liang-group-fss/<PROJECT_NAME>/build/
                                    <wrl FILES> ~/<INTENDED_DIRECTORIES>

2. upload to Rice obelix 
(in your case, you might be able to run freeWRL in your computer)

scp <wrl FILES> <YOUR_ID>@obelix.rice.edu:/home/<YOUR_ID>/<INTENDED_DIRECTORIES>

3. View in FreeWRL
./freewrl_43m_x64.AppImage <wrl FILE path>

